  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 orphan claim)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A supporting claim regarding mesh-independence is included; experimental validation evidence was reviewed during the assessment but the structured provenance link from that claim to the underlying evidence dataset was inadvertently omitted during package assembly.",
