      "name": "Mesh independence of hemolysis index predictions",
      "description": "The CFD hemolysis index predictions for the FDA generic centrifugal pump are mesh-independent at the selected spatial resolution of 8.4 million polyhedral cells, as determined by a three-level grid convergence study conducted under VAD operating conditions."
    }
