      "rationale": "Iterative residuals are reported but QOI convergence history for the hemolysis scalar was not tracked separately. Round-off error analysis was not performed. Factor not assessed at required depth; epistemic gap flagged at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
