      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup, boundary condition assignment, and post-processing scripts; documented checklist with sign-off.",
      "rationale": "No independent review of model setup or post-processing was performed. Analyst self-review only. Epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
