      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive law selection justified by physics-based arguments and sensitivity study; alternative model forms evaluated.",
      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected without comparison to alternative models (e.g., RSM or LES). Giersiepen hemolysis power law used without evaluation of Heuser–Opitz or Arora alternatives. Model form uncertainty not quantified. Epistemic gap. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
