      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material properties and boundary condition inputs documented with sources and uncertainty ranges; Monte Carlo propagation covers all significant inputs.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ covers blood viscosity and hemolysis power-law coefficients (C, α, β) but excludes pump wall roughness and inlet turbulence intensity, both of which have non-negligible sensitivity indices from a prior pilot study. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
