      "acceptanceCriteria": "Biological variability in donor blood samples characterised; minimum sample size justified by power analysis; batch effects documented.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro hemolysis experiments used pooled bovine blood from a single supplier batch. Donor variability and batch effects were not characterised. No power analysis for sample size. Epistemic gap. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
