      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency mapping between validation experiment inputs and COU inputs; any gaps in equivalency quantified and their impact on prediction uncertainty assessed.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency mapping was produced. The use of bovine blood in validation versus human blood in the COU introduces a known rheological discrepancy that was acknowledged in the report but not quantified. Epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
